sources.title: Desert Escape (1940) ACTION-MYSTERY
sources.description:
Stars: Warren Hull, Isabel Jewell, John Dilson
Director: Sam Newfield

A young medical-school graduate wrongly confined in prison. He escapes and finds a haven and romance in an Arizona small town. But his hopes of happiness and freedom are dashed when a gangster and his four henchmen show up.(a.k.a. Marked Men)
